                                       ---------------------------
                                             OfficeModel
                                       ---------------------------
                                          Daniel Sagenschneider
                                       ---------------------------

  The OfficeModel contains the Source models of OfficeFloor that are configured by the graphical editors and compiled into the OfficeFrame by the OfficeCompiler.
				       
  The classes of OfficeModel are generated by the OfficeModelGenerator from the xml configuration files.

  This is its own separate project to allow:

   * OfficeXml to access the model classes and their XML marshaling configuration to load from XML configuration

   * OfficeXml to be isolated as its own plug-in source for OfficeFrame

   * OfficeCompiler to use OfficeModel (and OfficeXml to load the models from XML)

